    <a href="#s2">Step 2: Choose a destination</a>
    <a href="#s3">Step 3: Choose when to go</a>
    <a href="#s4">Step 4: Choose an operator</a>
    <a href="#s5">Step 5: Choose your package format</a>
    <a href="#s6">Step 6: Budget &amp; what's included</a>
    <a href="#s7">Step 7: Book early &mdash; and why</a>
    <a href="#s8">Step 8: Travel, insurance &amp; getting there</a>
    <a href="#s9">Step 9: Prepare &amp; get your gear</a>
